{
    "key": 65,
    "texts": [
        "<p>火舌舔上你的双腿。你的眼中充满泪水。你被烟幕笼罩了;也许是你的想象，但你认为你感觉到铁链有一点点松动。你用尽全力挣扎，全然不顾铁链在你的手腕上拴得有多么牢固。</p>",
        "[guide-start]",
        "<p>你因为火焰受到1D6点耐久值伤害。如果你的耐久值因此归零，你就会失去意识，被烈焰烧死！否则，进行一次“力量”检定。</p>",
        "[guide-end]"
    ],
    "interactions": [
        { "text": "投掷1D6点耐久", "action": "action_adjust_attribute", "param": { "key": "HP", "delta": "-1d6" }, "show": "!flag_hp_reduced" },
        {
            "text": "力量检定",
            "action": "action_check",
            "param": {
                "key": "STR",
                "isSkill" : false,
                "level": "value",
                "onPass": [{ "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "STR", "level": "value" } }],
                "onFail": [{ "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "STR", "level": "value" } }]
            },
            "show": ["flag_check_unfinished", "!flag_hp_zero", "!flag_punish_dice"],
            "disabled": "!flag_hp_reduced"
        },
        {
            "text": "力量检定-惩罚骰x1",
            "action": "action_check",
            "param": {
                "key": "STR",
                "isSkill" : false,
                "level": "value",
                "bonus": -1,
                "onPass": [{ "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "STR", "level": "value" } }],
                "onFail": [{ "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "STR", "level": "value" } }]
            },
            "show": ["flag_check_unfinished", "!flag_hp_zero", "flag_punish_dice"],
            "disabled": "!flag_hp_reduced"
        }
    ],
    "options": [
        { "key": 0, "text": "继续", "show": ["flag_hp_reduced", "flag_hp_zero"] },
        { "key": 1, "text": "继续", "show": ["flag_hp_reduced", "!flag_hp_zero", "flag_check_passed"] },
        { "key": 2, "text": "继续", "show": ["flag_hp_reduced", "!flag_hp_zero", "flag_check_failed"] }
    ],
    "onleave": [
        { "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "STR", "level": "none" } }
    ]
}